// MultipleChoice
// A labeled select dropdown for single-option selection from a list.
// Supports both controlled and uncontrolled usage.

FUNCTION handleChange(e)
  Updates internal selected value state.
  Calls onChange with the newly selected value.

---

FUNCTION MultipleChoice(props) -> ReactNode                               EXPORT
  Renders a native select element with a label.
  Uses controlled value if provided; falls back to internal state.
  Includes a default "Select an option" placeholder as the first option.
